translations.SPLASH_COIN_COLLECTOR_TITLE:
Find Gold Coins during
 extra reveals to win big!
translations.INFO_POP_UP6: Find 3,4, or 5 COINS to unlock the Extra Reveals Bonus!
translations.INFO_POP_UP7: Pronađi 3,4 ili 5 simbola KOVANICA i aktiviraj bonus igru!
translations.SPLASH_EXTRA_REVEALS_TITLE:
Find 3 or more Platinum Coins
 to unlock extra reveals!
translations.BONUS_INFO_POP_UP_TEXT3:
When no reveals remain, win the prize reached on the prize meter
and return to the main game.
translations.BONUS_INFO_POP_UP_TEXT2:
Ako se u polju TVOJE eSREĆKE nalazi bar jedan od brojeva iz polja DOBITNI BROJEVI,
osvajaš dobitak u iznosu navedenom ispod tog polja.
translations.BONUS_INFO_POP_UP_TEXT4:
Kada su sve bonus igre odigrane, osvojeni iznosi dobitaka se zbrajaju
 i bonus igra je završena.
translations.BONUS_INFO_POP_UP_TEXT1:
If any of the numbers on YOUR TICKETS match the WINNING NUMBERS,
win the prize shown on that ticket.
translations.SPLASH_EXTRA_REVEALS_TEXT:
Pronađi 3 ili više platinastih
kovanica i aktiviraj bonus igru!
translations.SPLASH_COIN_COLLECTOR_TEXT:
Pronađi zlatne kovanice u
 bonus igri i osvoji veliki dobitak!
translations.SPLASH_BONUS_TEXT2:
Find 3 or more Platinum Coins
to unlock extra reveals!
translations.SPLASH_BONUS_TEXT1:
Pronađi 3 ili više platinastih kovanica
 i aktiviraj bonus igre!
